OL,3,CMPs call for more Goverment funding
OL,4,Cfor hospices
OL,6,FMPs are demanding that the government
OL,7,Fgive emergency funding for hospices
OL,8,Fand a commitment to reform how they
OL,9,Fare funded.
OL,11,FIn an open letter to the government
OL,12,Fsigned by 60 MPs, including Liverpool
OL,13,FWest Derby MP Ian Byrne, they say:
OL,14,F"The hospice sector's unsustainable
OL,15,Ffunding model has not withstood the
OL,16,Fcost of living crisis and hospices are
OL,17,Freducing services and making frontline
OL,18,Fstaff redundant as a result."
