OL,3,CMPs call for more Goverment funding
OL,4,Cfor hospices
OL,6,FHospices UK say one in five hospices
OL,7,Fhave already made service cuts or are
OL,8,Fplanning to in the coming months. With
OL,9,Fan industry that is already facing a
OL,10,F#60m financial shortfall, even before
OL,11,Fthe sector is hit by the rise in
OL,12,Fnational insurance contributions and
OL,13,Fthe minimum wage, many are worried.
