OL,3,CMPs call for more Goverment funding
OL,4,Cfor hospices
OL,6,FMarie Curie, the UK's leading end-of-
OL,7,Flife charity, has written to the
OL,8,FSecretary of State for Health and
OL,9,FSocial Care Wes Streeting stating the
OL,10,Frecently announced increase to
OL,11,Femployer National Insurance
OL,12,Fcontributions will cost the charity an
OL,13,Fadditional #2.92million a year and
OL,14,Fwarns that without further support,
OL,15,Fthe only option left will be to reduce
OL,16,Fservices.
