OL,3,CMPs call for more Goverment funding
OL,4,Cfor hospices
OL,6,FThey said: "Our incredibly generous
OL,7,Fsupporters did not donate their hard-
OL,8,Fearned money for us to simply hand it
OL,9,Fback to the Government in the form of
OL,10,Fa #3million tax bill."
OL,12,FHow are Hopices funded?
OL,14,FOn average, one-third of hospice
OL,15,Fincome comes from the government with
OL,16,Fthe remaining two-thirds raised by
OL,17,Ffundraising.
