OL,3,CMPs call for more Goverment funding
OL,4,Cfor hospices
OL,6,FLiverpool West Derby MP Ian Byrne told
OL,7,FParliament on 30 October that the
OL,8,Ffunding system was a 'broken model',
OL,9,Fhe went on to say: "Let me be clear
OL,10,Fthat I have the utmost respect for
OL,11,Fpeople who give up their time and
OL,12,Fmoney to support our hospices, but as
OL,13,Fone constituent said to me recently,
OL,14,F'We shouldn't have to sell charity
OL,15,Fcupcakes to make sure kids are cared
OL,16,Ffor'. But that is what is happening at
OL,17,Fthe moment."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
