OL,6,FCurrently 84% of hospices are in
OL,7,Fdeficit as most hospices are
OL,8,Findependent charitable organisations
OL,9,Fthat receive some statutory funding
OL,10,Ffrom the NHS
OL,12,FThis comes after the city of Liverpool
OL,13,Fand further affield came together to
OL,14,Fsave the baby hospice Zoe's Place and
OL,15,Fhelp them successfully raise more than
OL,16,F5 million pounds in 30 days to build a
OL,17,Fnew premises and stay open.
