OL,3,CMPs call for more Goverment funding
OL,4,Cfor hospices
OL,6,FThe baby hospice that cares for
OL,7,Fchildren with life-limiting conditions
OL,8,Ffrom birth to the age five said the
OL,9,Fcost of living had affected their
OL,10,Ffundraising efforts.
OL,12,FWhile Zoe's Place has been saved there
OL,13,Fare many hopices still under threat
OL,14,Fdue to financial pressures.
OL,16,FThe full letter is below:
