OL,3,CMPs call for more Goverment funding
OL,4,Cfor hospices
OL,6,F"We are writing to call on you to
OL,7,Fprovide emergency funding for the
OL,8,Fcharitable hospice sector and commit
OL,9,Fto long-term reform of the sector's
OL,10,Ffunding model. This is to prevent
OL,11,Ffurther cuts to frontline hospice
OL,12,Fservices and staff.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
