OL,3,CMPs call for more Goverment funding
OL,4,Cfor hospices
OL,6,F"On average, one-third of hospice
OL,7,Fincome comes from government with the
OL,8,Fremaining two-thirds raised by
OL,9,Ffundraising. The funding hospices
OL,10,Freceive from Integrated Care Boards
OL,11,F(ICBs) is also inconsistent and often
OL,12,Fdoes not reflect the cost of the
OL,13,Fservices hospices provide on behalf of
OL,14,Fthe NHS.
OL,16,F"The hospice sector's unsustainable
OL,17,Ffunding model has not withstood the
OL,18,Fcost of living crisis and hospices are
OL,19,Freducing services and making frontline
OL,20,Fstaff redundant as a result.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
