OL,3,CMPs call for more Goverment funding
OL,4,Cfor hospices
OL,6,F"Hospices can be a key partner in
OL,7,Fsupporting the Government to shift
OL,8,Fmore care into the community. Hospice
OL,9,Fservices keep people out of hospital
OL,10,Fwho do not need to be there and ensure
OL,11,Fthey can die in their place of choice
OL,12,Fwith the care they need.
OL,14,F"We call on you to provide short-term
OL,15,Ffunding to prevent more cuts in the
OL,16,Fsector and commit to working with
OL,17,FHospice UK on a long-term funding
OL,18,Fsolution for hospices that is fit for
OL,19,Fthe future."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
